room_title: Escape room "The Secret Temple" by Enigma Escape Rooms in Los Angeles
room_address: 7805 West Sunset Blvd #200, Los Angeles, CA 90046
room_description:
Find yourself entangled in the mysteries of the oldest most protected secret society on Earth. Its keepers have guarded their secrets for centuries and passed them through generations in their clandestine ritual meetings.
You are a team of reporters who've been tasked to find their secret temple and uncover the enigma they've been guarding for millenniums. You've dug deep and found yourself in their secret room - locked. They'll come for you in an hour. Will you get out?
